text: "Can't Make up My Mind" is a song by DJ/singer Sonique released in May 2003. The song reached number 17 in the UK Singles Charts, spending 4 weeks in the Top 75, while also charting in the Romanian Top 100 at 55. ==Track listings== #"Can't Make Up My Mind" (Original 7 Inch Mix) #"Can't Make Up My Mind" (Robbie Rivera Full Vocal) #"Can't Make Up My Mind" (Michael Woods Remix) #"Can't Make Up My Mind" (Sonique Platinum Dust Mix) #"Can't Make Up My Mind" (Video) ==Charts== {|class="wikitable sortable" !
